<div class="title">Destressing</div>
<div class="substance">Benzodiazepines - Clonazepam (Klonopin) & Lorazepam (Ativan)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=TeEb&Exact=1">TeEb</a></div>


